</style><h3 id="outline__1" class="wp-block-heading">近年の カバー社 (ホロライブプロダクション) への誹謗中傷事例</h3><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="w6oKSZqQFa"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-shirakami-fubuki-slandered-by-some-nijisanji-listeners-following-her-decision-to-appear-as-a-voice-actor-in-kamen-rider-movie/">VTuber 白上フブキ 「にじさんじ」一部視聴者から誹謗中傷か 映画「仮面ライダー」声優出演決定受け</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;VTuber 白上フブキ 「にじさんじ」一部視聴者から誹謗中傷か 映画「仮面ライダー」声優出演決定受け&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-shirakami-fubuki-slandered-by-some-nijisanji-listeners-following-her-decision-to-appear-as-a-voice-actor-in-kamen-rider-movie/embed/#?secret=dpPEd3ZFGf#?secret=w6oKSZqQFa" data-secret="w6oKSZqQFa" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" data-secret="yjPBGjJhu7"> <a href="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-sakamata-chloe-calls-for-attention-to-personal-dm-hoaxes-spreading-about-her/">VTuber 沙花叉クロヱ 自身に関する“個人DM”デマ拡散への注意を呼びかけ</a></blockquote><iframe class="wp-embedded-content" sandbox="allow-scripts" security="restricted" title="&#8220;VTuber 沙花叉クロヱ 自身に関する“個人DM”デマ拡散への注意を呼びかけ&#8221; &#8212; P2y.jp" src="https://p2y.jp/vtuber-sakamata-chloe-calls-for-attention-to-personal-dm-hoaxes-spreading-about-her/embed/#?secret=KoKNCKhUiE#?secret=yjPBGjJhu7" data-secret="yjPBGjJhu7" width="600" height="338" frameborder="0" marginwidth="0" marginheight="0" scrolling="no"></iframe></div></figure><figure class="wp-block-embed is-type-wp-embed is-provider-p-2-y-jp wp-block-embed-p-2-y-jp"><div class="wp-block-embed__wrapper"><blockquote class="wp-embedded-content" 